text: AWGE is an American creative agency and record label founded in 2014 by American artist ASAP Rocky. The label has signed acts including A$AP Rocky, Playboi Carti, FERG, Slowthai, ThotTwat, SNVRK, Key!, Smooky Margiela, A$AP Mob. AWGE has two rules: #1. Never reveal what AWGE means. #2. When in doubt, always refer to rule #1. Category:American music companies
title: AWGE
